            <!-- Tour Description -->
            <div class="tour-description">
                <h2>Experience Authentic Moroccan Hammam Wellness Tradition</h2>
                <p>Immerse yourself in the centuries-old Moroccan wellness tradition with an authentic <strong>Moroccan hammam Agadir</strong> experience! A hammam is much more than just a bath - it's a deeply cultural spa ritual that Moroccans have practiced for over 1,000 years. This traditional steam bath experience is the ultimate way to relax, detoxify, and rejuvenate while experiencing genuine Moroccan culture.</p>
                
                <p>Your <strong>hammam Agadir</strong> journey begins as you enter the beautiful traditional spa with its stunning Moroccan tilework and serene atmosphere. The multi-step ritual starts with relaxation in the warm steam room, allowing your body to sweat and pores to open. Next comes the luxurious black soap (savon noir) application - a traditional eucalyptus-infused soap that softens skin beautifully.</p>
                
                <p>The highlight of the <strong>traditional hammam Morocco</strong> experience is the invigorating full-body exfoliation using the kessa glove. Your skilled attendant removes dead skin cells, leaving your skin incredibly smooth and glowing. You'll be amazed at how much dead skin comes off! Finally, relax with a soothing argan oil massage that hydrates and nourishes your newly soft skin. This authentic Moroccan spa experience will leave you feeling completely refreshed!</p>

                <h3>What Makes Our Moroccan Hammam Experience Special?</h3>
                <p>Unlike touristy spa packages, our <strong>Agadir spa</strong> experience is 100% authentic - the same traditional hammam that Moroccan families have enjoyed for generations. We use only natural products: pure savon noir (black soap), traditional kessa gloves, and certified organic Moroccan argan oil. Our experienced attendants (separate male and female professionals) are trained in proper traditional techniques.</p>
                
                <p>We offer both private hammam sessions for those wanting complete privacy, and traditional shared hammam experiences (still gender-separated) where you can observe how locals enjoy this ritual. Your attendant explains each step of the process, ensures your comfort, and adapts the intensity to your preferences - gentle for sensitive skin or vigorous for deep exfoliation!</p>
                
                <p>The <strong>Moroccan bath Agadir</strong> experience is perfect for anyone wanting authentic cultural immersion, wellness seekers, couples enjoying spa time, and those curious about traditional Moroccan rituals. No previous hammam experience needed - your attendant guides you through everything!</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Detailed Itinerary -->
            <div class="itinerary-section">
                <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1F2937; margin-bottom: 30px;">The Hammam Ritual: Step-by-Step Experience</h2>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 1: 15-20 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Arrival & Welcome at Traditional Hammam</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Arrive at the traditional hammam spa. You'll be welcomed by your attendant and given disposable undergarments (required). Store your belongings in a locker, and prepare to enter the warm steam rooms. Your attendant explains the ritual process and what to expect. Separate areas for men and women ensure comfort and privacy.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 2: 15-20 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Steam Room Relaxation - Opening the Pores</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Enter the warm, humid steam room (around 40-45°C). Relax on heated marble benches as the steam opens your pores and begins the detoxification process. Feel tension melting away as your body sweats out impurities. Your attendant may pour warm water over you to enhance the steam effect. This is the preparation phase - simply breathe deeply and relax!</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 3: 10-15 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Black Soap (Savon Noir) Application</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">Your attendant applies generous amounts of traditional black soap all over your body. This luxurious eucalyptus-infused soap is rich in vitamin E and softens the skin. You'll sit in the steam for another 10-15 minutes as the soap works its magic, further opening pores and preparing skin for exfoliation. The eucalyptus aroma is incredibly relaxing!</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 4: 20-30 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Vigorous Exfoliation with Kessa Glove - The Main Event!</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">The most transformative part! Your skilled attendant uses the traditional kessa exfoliating glove to scrub your entire body vigorously. Watch in amazement as dead skin rolls off - it's incredibly satisfying! This deep exfoliation reveals baby-soft, glowing skin underneath. The attendant focuses on rough areas (elbows, knees, heels) and adjusts pressure to your comfort. You'll be rinsed with warm water multiple times throughout this process.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 5: 10 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Hair Wash with Ghassoul Clay (Optional)</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">If desired, your attendant will wash your hair with traditional Moroccan ghassoul clay - a natural mineral clay that cleanses and conditions hair beautifully. This volcanic clay is rich in minerals and leaves hair soft and shiny. Scalp massage included! This step is optional and can be skipped if you prefer.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 6: 20-30 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Argan Oil Massage - Pure Relaxation</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">The grand finale! Move to the massage area for a full-body massage using pure Moroccan argan oil. Your therapist uses traditional techniques to relax muscles, improve circulation, and hydrate your freshly exfoliated skin. The argan oil is quickly absorbed, leaving skin soft, smooth, and glowing - not greasy! This is pure bliss after the invigorating scrub.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="itinerary-item">
                    <div class="itinerary-time">Step 7: 15 minutes</div>
                    <h4 class="itinerary-title">Rest & Moroccan Mint Tea</h4>
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.8;">After your massage, relax in the cooling room or lounge area. Enjoy complimentary traditional Moroccan mint tea and perhaps light snacks. Take your time getting dressed - there's no rush! Feel how incredibly soft and smooth your skin is. Many guests say this is the softest their skin has ever felt. Complete relaxation and rejuvenation!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

