                        <li><strong>Optional:</strong> Your own swimsuit if more comfortable than disposables</li>
                        <li><strong>Flip-flops:</strong> For walking in wet areas (can also be provided)</li>
                        <li><strong>Change of clothes:</strong> Fresh clothes for after the hammam</li>
                        <li><strong>Hair tie:</strong> If you have long hair and don't want clay wash</li>
                        <li><strong>Cash:</strong> For tips and optional product purchases</li>
